{"tid":390459,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局證蔡若蓮兒子死訊　楊潤雄：感難過會與副局同行","createTime":"2017-09-07T06:10:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T09:12:52.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0dea1659a4ab1e7c059eef12c8cb0694b116cba7","tid":390459,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170907/large/1504759290_4ae8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170907%2Flarge%2F1504759290_4ae8.jpg&h=101df4a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n教育局副局長蔡若蓮的兒子今早在油麻地柯士甸道擎天半島墮樓身亡。教育局證實其死訊，局長楊潤雄稱對事件深感難過和惋惜，並代表教育局全體同事向蔡若蓮和她的家人致以最深切慰問。楊又稱，「我們會全力支持副局長，與她同行，度過困難的時刻。」<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"1eb88a7777d4ae76caaa6e5aae7fe8edc04e2abe","tid":390459,"uid":54264,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 楊局長驚唔驚"},{"pid":"1d414c74012b187e46f716ab86eab8b4c3da16e0","tid":390459,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:13:23.000Z","msg":"信黨的人有禍了"},{"pid":"1f4a7b710b0341bcff3ed315c74d85b9cf0a362a","tid":390459,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:14:28.000Z","msg":"局長想同行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77e3040feb634abb0f618a8f229a3ff14f85cb9","tid":390459,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:15:13.000Z","msg":"同佢個仔同行"},{"pid":"5287fca0cc33f1b12011e237305b1d2672ea9c21","tid":390459,"uid":49197,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:15:37.000Z","msg":"佢就正啦,今晚借D意